#: ../../source/introduction/welcome/about_document.rst:2
msgid "1.1 About This Documentation"
msgstr "1.1 关于本文档"

#: ../../source/introduction/welcome/about_document.rst:4
msgid ""
"This document is the official user and administrator guide for "
"**FlowPilot**, a self-hosted, workflow-based ticketing system. It is "
"designed to help you understand, install, configure, and effectively use "
"FlowPilot to manage your team's requests and processes."
msgstr ""
"本文件是 **FlowPilot** 的官方用户和管理员手册，这是一款自托管、基于流程的工单系统。旨在帮助你理解、安装、配置并高效使用 "
"FlowPilot 来管理团队的请求和流程。"

#: ../../source/introduction/welcome/about_document.rst:7
msgid "Purpose & Scope"
msgstr "目的与范围"

#: ../../source/introduction/welcome/about_document.rst:9
msgid ""
"This guide covers all aspects of the system, from initial installation "
"and core concepts to daily operations and advanced administrative "
"configurations. It is intended for:"
msgstr "本指南涵盖系统的各个方面，从初始安装、核心概念到日常运营以及高级管理配置。适用于："

#: ../../source/introduction/welcome/about_document.rst:11
#: ../../source/introduction/who_need_read.rst:6
msgid "**End Users** - Who submit and handle tickets in their daily work"
msgstr "**终端用户** —— 日常提交和处理工单的用户"

#: ../../source/introduction/welcome/about_document.rst:12
msgid ""
"**Administrators & Implementers** - Who are responsible for deploying, "
"customizing, and maintaining the FlowPilot instance"
msgstr "**管理员与实施者** —— 负责部署、定制和维护 FlowPilot 实例"

#: ../../source/introduction/welcome/about_document.rst:13
msgid ""
"**IT Managers** - Who need to understand the system's capabilities to "
"align it with business processes"
msgstr "**IT 经理** —— 需要了解系统能力以与业务流程对齐"

#: ../../source/introduction/welcome/about_document.rst:16
msgid "Document Structure"
msgstr "文档结构"

#: ../../source/introduction/welcome/about_document.rst:18
msgid ""
"The documentation is organized into logical parts to help you find "
"information quickly:"
msgstr "文档按逻辑部分组织，便于你快速找到信息："

#: ../../source/introduction/welcome/about_document.rst:20
msgid "**Part 1: Introduction** — high-level overview and quick-start guides"
msgstr "**第 1 部分：引言** — 高层概览与快速入门指南"

#: ../../source/introduction/welcome/about_document.rst:21
msgid ""
"**Part 2: Installation & Deployment** — technical guides for setting up "
"your FlowPilot instance"
msgstr "**第 2 部分：安装与部署** — 搭建 FlowPilot 实例的技术指南"

#: ../../source/introduction/welcome/about_document.rst:22
msgid ""
"**Part 3: Core Concepts** — fundamental ideas behind FlowPilot's workflow "
"engine"
msgstr "**第 3 部分：核心概念** — FlowPilot 工作流引擎的基础理念"

#: ../../source/introduction/welcome/about_document.rst:23
msgid ""
"**Part 4: Administrator Guide** — configuring workflows, permissions, and"
" integrations"
msgstr "**第 4 部分：管理员指南** — 配置流程、权限与集成"

#: ../../source/introduction/welcome/about_document.rst:24
msgid "**Part 5: User Guide** — daily tasks for creating and managing tickets"
msgstr "**第 5 部分：用户指南** — 创建和管理工单的日常操作"

#: ../../source/introduction/welcome/about_document.rst:25
msgid "**Part 6: FAQ & Troubleshooting** — common questions and issue resolution"
msgstr "**第 6 部分：常见问题与故障排查** — 常见问答与问题解决"

#: ../../source/introduction/welcome/about_document.rst:26
msgid ""
"**Part 7: Appendices** — supplementary information such as glossaries and"
" integration setups"
msgstr "**第 7 部分：附录** — 补充信息，如术语表和集成配置"

#: ../../source/introduction/welcome/about_document.rst:29
msgid "Conventions Used"
msgstr "文档约定"

#: ../../source/introduction/welcome/about_document.rst:31
msgid ""
"To improve readability, we use the following conventions throughout this "
"guide:"
msgstr "为提高可读性，本文档使用以下约定："

#: ../../source/introduction/welcome/about_document.rst:34
msgid "Text Formatting"
msgstr "文本格式"

#: ../../source/introduction/welcome/about_document.rst:36
msgid ""
"**Bold Text** - Used to highlight key interface elements, such as buttons"
" (**Submit**), menu items (**Settings**), or page titles (**My Tickets**)"
msgstr "**粗体** —— 用于突出关键界面元素，如按钮（**提交**）、菜单项（**设置**）或页面标题（**我的工单**）"

#: ../../source/introduction/welcome/about_document.rst:39
msgid ""
"``Code / Monospace Font`` - Indicates file names, configuration "
"parameters, database commands, or code snippets (e.g., ``DEBUG = False``,"
" ``docker-compose up``)"
msgstr ""
"``代码/等宽字体`` —— 表示文件名、配置参数、数据库命令或代码片段（如 ``DEBUG = False``、``docker-compose"
" up``）"

#: ../../source/introduction/welcome/about_document.rst:43
msgid "Admonitions"
msgstr "提示框"

#: ../../source/introduction/welcome/about_document.rst:47
msgid "Provides additional information or tips that are helpful but not critical."
msgstr "提供额外信息或提示，虽非关键但有帮助。"

#: ../../source/introduction/welcome/about_document.rst:51
msgid "Highlights crucial information required for a task to succeed."
msgstr "强调任务成功所需的重要信息。"

#: ../../source/introduction/welcome/about_document.rst:55
msgid "Indicates a potential risk of data loss or configuration error."
msgstr "提示可能导致数据丢失或配置错误的风险。"

#: ../../source/introduction/welcome/about_document.rst:58
msgid "Feedback and Support"
msgstr "反馈与支持"

#: ../../source/introduction/welcome/about_document.rst:60
msgid ""
"We strive to keep this documentation accurate and helpful. If you find "
"any errors, have suggestions for improvements, or encounter topics that "
"need more clarification, please reach out through our official support "
"channels."
msgstr "我们致力于保持文档的准确与实用。若发现错误、有改进建议，或需要更详细的说明，请通过官方支持渠道联系我们。"

#: ../../source/introduction/welcome/about_document.rst:64
msgid ""
"The software and this documentation are subject to continuous "
"improvement. Please refer to the version information at the beginning of "
"this document to ensure you are consulting the correct guide for your "
"installed version of FlowPilot."
msgstr "软件和文档都在持续改进。请查看文档开头的版本信息，确保你查看的指南与已安装的 FlowPilot 版本匹配。"

#: ../../source/introduction/welcome/about_flowpilot.rst:2
msgid "1.2 About Flowpilot"
msgstr "1.2 关于 Flowpilot"

#: ../../source/introduction/welcome/about_flowpilot.rst:4
msgid ""
"Flowpilot is an open-source process automation platform developed based on"
" Django. After multiple versions of iteration and refactoring, we proudly"
" present Flowpilot 3.0 - a version that achieves a qualitative leap in "
"visualization, flexibility, and scalability."
msgstr ""
"Flowpilot 是基于 Django 开发的开源流程自动化平台。经过多次迭代与重构，我们自豪地推出 Flowpilot "
"3.0——在可视化、灵活性和可扩展性上实现了质的飞跃。"

#: ../../source/introduction/welcome/getting_help.rst:2
msgid "1.3 Get Help & Community Support"
msgstr "1.3 获取帮助与社区支持"

#: ../../source/introduction/welcome/getting_help.rst:4
msgid ""
"📝 GitHub Issues - Submit bug reports and feature requests. "
"https://github.com/abubakar668/flowpilot/issues"
msgstr "📝 GitHub Issues - 提交缺陷与功能需求：https://github.com/abubakar668/flowpilot/issues"

#: ../../source/introduction/welcome/getting_help.rst:5
msgid "💬 Discussion Forum Discord. https://discord.gg/WuppaG638k"
msgstr "💬 讨论论坛 Discord：https://discord.gg/WuppaG638k"

#: ../../source/introduction/welcome/getting_help.rst:6
msgid ""
"📧 Commercial Support & Customization: For enterprise-level deep "
"customization, technical training, or deployment support needs, please "
"contact me at [abubakarkhalid637@gmail.com;abubakarkhalid637@gmail.com]."
msgstr ""
"📧 商业支持与定制：如需企业级深度定制、技术培训或部署支持，请联系 "
"[abubakarkhalid637@gmail.com;abubakarkhalid637@gmail.com]。"

#: ../../source/introduction/welcome/getting_help.rst:7
msgid "💰 Member Benefits. See https://patreon.com/abubakar668 for more details."
msgstr "💰 会员权益：详见 https://github.com/abubakar668/flowpilot/blob/master/README_zh.md"

